Package: SpaTME
Type: Package
Title: SpaTME: Deciphering tumor microenvironment spatial characteristics and linking them with patient phenotypes
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Xiaojie Cheng
Maintainer: Xiaojie Cheng <lvlanzi0306@gmail.com>
Description: SpaTME is a novel framework that utilizes spatial transcriptomics data to provide a comprehensive characterization of the TME across molecular, cellular, and tissue structure levels. Specifically, SpaTME aims to link the spatial features of TME with patient prognosis using bulk RNA-seq profiles annotated with clinical information.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
